high_descs: Walk towards the purple wall, then turn right and walk over to the white desk.
Pick up the black pen off of the white desk.
Turn around and walk towards the black trash can, then turn left and walk over to the tall white dresser next to the bed.
Put the pen in the grey bowl on the dresser.
Pick up the grey bowl with the pen in it off of the dresser.
Turn around and walk over to the far wall, then turn right to face the desk.
Put the grey bowl with the pen in it on the desk to the right of the blue pencil.
anns.task_desc: Put a grey bowl with a black pen in it on the desk.

high_descs: Move forward to the box, turn right, go to the pen on the desk.
Pick up the pen on the desk.
Turn right, bring the pen to the tall white dresser, left of the bed.
Put the pen in the bowl on the dresser.
Pick up the bowl with pen on the dresser.
Turn around, bring the bowl back to the desk on the right.
Put the bowl with pen on the desk, left of the watch.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a pen in it, on the desk.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then move forward. Turn left then right again and face the desk.
Pick the pen from the desk.
Turn to the right and go forward to the dresser.
Place the pen in the bowl.
Pick up the pen and bowl from the shelf.
Turn to the left and go forward. Turn to the right and face the desk.
Place the bowl and pen on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl and pen on to a desk.
